name: Mini Magnetic Vase (plants not included)
description:
Add a bit of delightful charm to your fridge, or any other magnetic surface, with these darling little vases. There are several great styles to pick from, including ceramic and glass options, so you can create a mini garden all of your own. Pick out your favorite vases, add your own plants, create your mini magnetic garden display or create the perfect gift for your someone special. These are perfect fun little magnetic vases.
Adorable design, with magnetic backing
Offered in 8 design options, plants not included
Package list: 1 tiny vase, in choice of design
